<%= @user_from.name %> has booked a case appointment with you on <%= @event.datetime.strftime("%A %e %B at %I:%M%p") %>
=============================================

You'll be sent an email to remind you about the appointment 2 hours before it starts.

<%- unless @event.book_id_partnertoprepare.blank? %>
  The case that <%=@user_from.first_name %> would like you to prepare is attached with this email - be sure to read it thoroughly before you start the case:

  <%= @book_partnertoprepare.author.split(' ')[0] + " - " + @book_partnertoprepare.title %>

<%- end %>

If you would like #{@user_from.first_name} to prepare a case for you, click the link below to choose one.

::Choose case for event link::

If you're ready to start the case now, call <%=@user_from.first_name %> using the button below

<%=
  link_to "skype:#{@user_from.skype}?call", "data-original-title"=>"Call #{@user_from.first_name} on Skype" do
    image_tag "https://www.casenexus.com/assets/icons/skype_button.png"
    + "Call #{@user_from.first_name} now"
  end
%>

<%- unless @event.book_id_partnertoprepare.blank? %>

  And if you want to start as the interviewer now, use this button to go to the case console, where you can concurrently view the case PDF , and a feedback form for #{@user_from.first_name}:

  <%= 
    link_to "https://www.casenexus.com/console?friend_id=" + @event.partner.id.to_s + "&book_id=" + @book_partnertoprepare.id.to_s do
      "Start case now as Interviewer"
    end
  %>
    
<%- else %>

  And if you want to start as the interviewer now, use this button to go to the case console, where you can select a case to give, and fill out a feedback form for #{@user_from.first_name}:

  <%= 
    link_to "https://www.casenexus.com/console?friend_id=" + @event.partner.id.to_s do
      "Start case now as Interviewer"
    end
  %>

<%- end %>

To see the appointment, use the link below

<%= @url %>
